## Configuration

- **Secrets:** {{SECRETS_METHOD}} (e.g., environment variables, never committed)
- **Non-secret config:** {{CONFIG_METHOD}} (e.g., config files, env vars with defaults)
- **Environment file:** `.env` (copy `.env.example` to `.env`, fill in values)
